 results, e.g. `fact_main_theorem`; leave the value blank to let the skill
 auto-infer the deepest terminal facts>

The paper is written from the transitive-predecessor CLOSURE of these targets
(NOT every proven fact) and the reference ledger is seeded from the SAME closure,
so the writer's facts and the bibliography agree. Blank = the skill guesses the
deepest terminal facts (facts nothing else depends on) and records that it guessed.

